黯黑史詩是傾向[[哥德金屬|哥德金屬]]的[[交響金屬|交響金屬]]樂團，並在後期受到[[死亡金屬|死亡金屬]]的影響，逐漸融入了[[旋律死亡金屬|旋律死亡金屬]]的元素<ref name=Cioppa>{{cite book|last=Della Cioppa |first=Gianni|title=Heavy metal: i contemporanei|publisher={{link-en|Giunti Editore|Giunti Editore}}|date=2010|isbn=978-8809749627}}</ref><ref name=rafabasa>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rafabasa.com/2014/04/22/critica-del-cd-de-epica-the-quantum-enigma/ |title=Crítica del CD de EPICA - The Quantum Enigma {{!}} WWW.RAFABASA.COM - Noticias en español sobre el heavy metal y los grupos de heavy metal |accessdate=2017-05-30 |archive-date=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117021908/http://www.rafabasa.com/2014/04/22/critica-del-cd-de-epica-the-quantum-enigma/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lagrosseradio.com/metal/webzine-metal/chronique-metal/p8789-epica-the-quantum-enigma.html |title=Epica - The Quantum Enigma - Chronique - La Grosse Radio Metal - Ecouter du Metal - Webzine Metal |accessdate=2017-05-30 |archive-date=2014-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429044643/http://www.lagrosseradio.com/metal/webzine-metal/chronique-metal/p8789-epica-the-quantum-enigma.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。從第三張專輯開始，[[前衛金屬|前衛金屬]]的特徵也開始變得明顯<ref name=Cioppa/><ref name="musicaldiscoveries.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.musicaldiscoveries.com/reviews/epica2008.htm|title = Epica The Divine Conspiracy}}</ref><ref name=ashladan>{{Cite web |url=http://ashladan.be/metal-reviews/epica-the-quantum-enigma |title=Epica - The Quantum Enigma {{!}} Ashladan |access-date=2017-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429191103/http://ashladan.be/metal-reviews/epica-the-quantum-enigma |archive-date=2014-04-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。此外，他們也時常運用[[鞭擊金屬|鞭擊金屬]]和[[蠱戮金屬|蠱戮金屬]]的[[即興重覆段|即興重覆段]]、[[黑金屬|黑金屬]]的過門、短暫浮現的[[力量金屬|力量金屬]]段落和[[阿拉伯音樂|阿拉伯音樂]]<ref name="thisisnotascene.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.thisisnotascene.com/2014/epica-the-quantum-enigma/ |title=Epica - The Quantum Enigma » ThisIsNotAScene - Music Reviews, Interviews & News |accessdate=2017-05-30 |archive-date=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117022950/http://www.thisisnotascene.com/2014/epica-the-quantum-enigma/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MetalUndergroundRFTI">{{cite web|url= http://www.metalunderground.com/reviews/details.cfm?releaseid=6192|title= Recensione di "Requiem for the Indifferent" su Metal Underground|accessdate= 2017-05-30|archive-date= 2012-09-08|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/6AW2jUgrX?url=http://www.metalunderground.com/reviews/details.cfm?releaseid=6192|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="MI">{{Cite web|url = http://www.metalitalia.com/articolo/epica-il-nuovo-album-the-holographic-principle-traccia-per-traccia-e-intervista-a-simone-simons/|title = EPICA: il nuovo album "The Holographic Principle" traccia per traccia e intervista a Simone Simons!|editor = MetalItalia.com|date =2016-07-28}}</ref><ref name="Biani">{{Cite magazine|title = Epica: The Holographic Principle (listening session)|magazine = MyRock|editor = BMS Soc. coop.|date = 2016-07-08|p = 5}}</ref><ref name="WLM">{{Cite web|url = http://www.welovemetal.com/newsite/wordpress/2016/08/10/album-review-epica-the-holographic-principle/|title = Epica – The Holographic|date = 2016-08-10|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171009194237/http://www.welovemetal.com/newsite/wordpress/2016/08/10/album-review-epica-the-holographic-principle/|archivedate = 2017-10-09|df = |accessdate = 2017-05-30}}</ref>。一些歌曲還有[[電子音樂|電子音樂]]元素、{{link-en|結構金屬|Djent}}變調，以及源自[[中東|中東]]、[[中國|中國]]和[[凱爾特音樂|凱爾特]][[民謠金屬|民謠金屬]]的旋律<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.truemetal.it/news/epica-mark-jansen-simone-simons-68982|title = Epica (Mark Jansen & Simone Simons)|editor = TrueMetal.it|date = 2014-05-27}}</ref>。黯黑史詩也以優美厚實的女性古典唱腔著名，與富有侵略力量的金屬樂互相交織，形成非常流行、容易掌握、氣勢恢弘、情感濃郁的複雜旋律<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.metal.de/interviews/listening-session-zum-neuen-epica-album-the-holographic-principle-188775/ |title = Epica - Zuviel gibt es für EPICA nicht: Die Listening-Session zu "The Holographic Principle"|editor = Metal.de|date = 2016-08-07}}</ref><ref>{{YouTube|Ij4mluF1jfI|SPARK TV: EPICA - interview with Mark Jansen about upcoming new album "The Holographic Principle"|date = 2016-07-19}}</ref>。在樂團的[[人聲|人聲]]表現中，[[席夢娜·西蒙斯|席夢娜·西蒙斯]]和[[馬可·傑生|馬可·揚森]]分別使用女性清腔和男性{{link-en|死腔|Death growl}}，形成歌劇《[[美女與野獸|美女與野獸]]》、天使與魔鬼般的衝突感<ref name="Chad"/>。

樂團的前任吉他手亞德·斯盧傑特表示：「黯黑史詩是力量金屬與哥德金屬之間的一座橋梁」<ref>{{cite web |author=Cursed With Oblivion |title=Interview with Mark Jansen, Simone Simons and Ad Sluijter of Epica |url=http://www.xs4all.nl/~cursed/epica-interview.htm |publisher=Xs4all.nl/~cursed |accessdate=2008-03-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080116110425/http://www.xs4all.nl/~cursed/epica-interview.htm |archivedate=2008-01-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主唱席夢娜·西蒙斯表示偏愛人們把黯黑史詩歸類為交響金屬<ref>{{cite web |author=Rademacher, Brian |title=Interview with Simone Simons of Epica |url=http://www.rockeyez.com/interviews/int-epica-simons.html |publisher=Rockeyez.com |accessdate=2008-03-30}}</ref>。而樂團的創始人馬可·揚森說：「我們不介意被稱作哥德金屬」<ref>{{cite web |author=Vayner, Ofer |title=Interview with Mark Jensen of Epica |url=http://www.alternative-zine.com/interviews/en/76 |publisher=Alternative-zine.com |accessdate=2008-03-30 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106214534/http://alternative-zine.com/interviews/en/76 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他將黯黑史詩描述為「交響死亡金屬」，是死亡金屬和交響金屬之間的橋樑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spaziorock.it/intervista.php?id=127|title=SpazioRock - Interviste - Epica (Mark Jansen)|work=SpazioRock|accessdate=2017-05-30|archive-date=2012-09-10|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120910115052/http://www.spaziorock.it/intervista.php?id=127|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.truemetal.it/cont/news/epica-mark-jansen/16819/1.html|title=Epica (Mark Jansen)|work=TrueMetal}}{{Dead link|date=2020年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。黯黑史詩的音樂具有侵略性和誇飾的成分<ref>{{cite web |author=Van der Wal, Kim |title=''The Divine Conspiracy'' Review |url=http://www.lordsofmetal.nl/showreview.php?id=10237&lang=en |publisher=Lordsofmetal.nl |accessdate=2008-03-30 |archive-date=2011-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927003809/http://www.lordsofmetal.nl/showreview.php?id=10237&lang=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，有時是極端的浮華<ref name="Fox">{{cite web |author=Fox, Keith |url=http://www.metalreview.com/4074/Epica-The-Divine-Conspiracy.aspx |title=''The Divine Conspiracy'' Review |publisher=Metalreview.com |accessdate=2008-03-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080302041124/http://www.metalreview.com/4074/Epica-The-Divine-Conspiracy.aspx |archivedate=2008-03-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。一些歌曲是「如史詩般盛大、雄偉的」，而另一些則是「更加柔和、感傷」的歌曲<ref name="Chad"/>。樂團也帶有前衛音樂的元素<ref name="AMG Consign">{{cite web |author=Rivadavia, Eduardo |title=''Consign to Oblivion'' Review |url={{Allmusic|class=album|id=r795285|pure_url=yes}} |publisher=Allmusic |accessdate=2008-03-30}}</ref>，並有很多哥德式氣氛和多愁善感的情緒<ref name="Fox"/><ref name="Chad"/>。

黯黑史詩運用許多交響金屬和哥德金屬樂團標誌性的極端手法，一方面運用殘暴低沉的死腔、黑腔與吼腔，另一方面又用空靈優美的女聲旋律，形成強烈的兩極對比<ref name="Fox"/>。美國線上音樂資料庫[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]音樂評論家{{link-en|愛德里·瓦達維亞|Eduardo Rivadavia}}表示：「黯黑史詩的吸引力來自『光明』與『黑暗』兩種極端聲音，他們一直在探索這種衝突的美學。而強大的吉他[[即興重覆段|即興重覆段]]與快速靈活的鼓點編排，造成另一股高聳厚重的衝擊戲劇性，這與管弦樂和鍵盤所堆疊出的悅耳音樂又持續互相衝擊」<ref>{{cite web |author=Rivadavia, Eduardo |title=''Divine Conspiracy'' Review |url={{Allmusic|class=album|id=r1183427|pure_url=yes}} |publisher=Allmusic.com |accessdate=2008-03-30}}</ref>。

主唱席夢娜·西蒙斯雖然是以[[次女高音|次女高音]]音域的歌劇式唱腔為中心<ref name="AMG Consign"/>，但有時她也會演唱「毫無瑕疵、帶有豐富情感的純淨[[女低音|女低音]]」<ref name="Chad"/>。不過，席夢娜·西蒙斯認為早年錯認自己的音域是次女高音，事實上她應該是[[女高音|女高音]]<ref name="Epica - Live Fan Q&A Interview 2014">{{cite web|title=Simone confirms to be a soprano|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Td1NK_fi6M|date=2014-04-08|accessdate=2017-05-30}}</ref>。馬可·揚森的死腔雖然是用來襯托席夢娜·西蒙斯的天籟歌聲，但是他呈現出的陽剛邪氣也非常重要，這對於音樂的平衡度和多樣性上具有同等的價值<ref name="Chad">{{cite web |author=Bowar, Chad |title=''The Divine Conspiracy'' Review |url=http://heavymetal.about.com/od/cdreviews/fr/epicadivine.htm |publisher=About.com |accessdate=2008-03-30 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106214508/http://heavymetal.about.com/od/cdreviews/fr/epicadivine.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。黯黑史詩也因為廣泛使用[[管弦樂團|管弦樂團]]和[[歌劇|歌劇]][[合唱|唱詩班]]而聞名<ref name="AMG Consign"/>。而在歌詞主題上，經常涉及[[哲學|哲學]]、[[心理|心理]]、[[精神|精神]]、[[社會|社會]]、[[政治|政治]]和個人情感。他們也很重視[[詞彙|詞彙]]在音樂上的裝飾，例如吟誦字句和演唱[[拉丁語|拉丁語]]、[[阿拉伯語|阿拉伯語]]或[[希伯來語|希伯來語]]的歌詞<ref name="AMG Phantom">{{cite web |author=Rivadavia, Eduardo |title=''The Phantom Agony'' Review |url={{Allmusic|class=album|id=r674057|pure_url=yes}} |publisher=Allmusic.com |accessdate=2008-03-30}}</ref>。
